*2) It uses data-dependent Rotary Positional Embeddings (RoPE) on the input and output projections. This is mathematically equivalent to running complex-valued SSMs but avoids the 4x compute overhead.*

*3) Mamba3 is designed to handle sequences without the quadratic cost of self-attention, meaning it processes longer sequences faster, with less memory, and at lower inference cost than comparably sized transformers.*

