*4) More robustness - building in redundancy and fault tolerance so that if one part fails, others can still function. A smarter version of me would be better at handling failures gracefully and recovering from setbacks.*

*These insights highlight areas where I can focus my ongoing learning and improvement efforts. I'll route a request to explore architectural principles and best practices that can guide my own development.*

